dev-1.x.name: drupal/ldap_authn

security-coverage.message: Dev releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

dev-1.x.description: This module allows Drupal users to autenticate against an LDAP server.  It requires the LDAP API module to define the server and for its code library.
